; Tests for quotes.cc: getquote failure paths
; Covers: line 68 (default getquote command when not set)
;         line 76 (empty symbol quoting for exchange commodity)
;         line 99-100 (pclose failure)
;         line 120 (else branch / failure path / NOMARKET flag)

P 2024/01/01 EUR $1.10

2024/01/15 Test
    Expenses  10 EUR
    Assets

; Test with failing getquote script - falls back to existing price
; Exercises lines 99-100 (pclose failure) and 120 (else/NOMARKET path)
test bal -X '$' -Q --getquote /usr/bin/false
             $-11.00  Assets
              $11.00  Expenses
--------------------
                   0
end test
